  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/2351",
  "title": "Document __hitIndex",
  "body": "when using the `item` template, we add a special property to each hit `__hitIndex` ([code](https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/blob/5cd002b0c2442cc952d59cecab335a55e61cbd35/src/components/Hits.js#L13)). This property makes it easy to number the items in a hits widget.\r\n\r\nBut this property is not documented, I didn't know about it before a [user found it again](https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/issues/2347). We should document it!",
